<br>
If anything mages should complain about, is NPC ench should be limited to 2 charmed mage pets. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  Just thought this was pretty amuzing. <p>Vocerate Summoneer<BR>
